OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784432922
OL,3,CUkrainian drones hit warehouses of
OL,4,CRussia's largest online retailer and
OL,5,Coil site
OL,7,FNine people have been killed, and more
OL,8,Fthan 80 wounded, in Ukrainian drone
OL,9,Fstrikes that struck two sprawling
OL,10,Fwarehouses and oil infrastructure in
OL,11,FRussia on Saturday afternoon,
OL,12,Faccording to officials.
OL,14,FKyiv's forces have pressed their
OL,15,Frelentless aerial campaign against
OL,16,Fenergy infrastructure and military
OL,17,Ftargets inside Russia, aiming to
OL,18,Fundermine Moscow's war effort, more
OL,19,Fthan five years on from the full-scale
OL,20,Finvasion of Ukraine.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
