OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784432922
OL,3,CUkrainian drones hit warehouses of
OL,4,CRussia's largest online retailer and
OL,5,Coil site
OL,7,FTwo warehouses of one of Russia's
OL,8,Flargest online retailers, Wildberries,
OL,9,Fwere hit by Ukrainian drones
OL,10,Fovernight, according to Russian
OL,11,Fofficials ` one in the town of
OL,12,FKotovsk, some 220 miles from the
OL,13,Fborder with Ukraine, and another in
OL,14,Fthe city of Elektrostal, about 30
OL,15,Fmiles east of Moscow.
OL,17,FImages and footage released by Russian
OL,18,Fonline outlets showed a fire raging at
OL,19,Fthe Elektrostal facility, with massive
OL,20,Fplumes of smoke towering over it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784432922
OL,3,CUkrainian drones hit warehouses of
OL,4,CRussia's largest online retailer and
OL,5,Coil site
OL,7,FA Ukrainian drone also hit an oil
OL,8,Fdepot in the city of Noginsk, just
OL,9,Fnorth of Elektrostal, sparking a fire
OL,10,Fand prompting evacuations of a nearby
OL,11,Fmaternity hospital and a residential
OL,12,Fbuilding, according to the governor of
OL,13,Fthe Moscow region, Andrei Vorobyov.
OL,15,FDrone debris also hit a kindergarten
OL,16,Fbuilding, Vorobyov said, sparking a
OL,17,Ffire that has since been put out.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
