CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784432922
OL,3,CUkrainian drones hit warehouses of
OL,4,CRussia's largest online retailer and
OL,5,Coil site
OL,7,FSeven night shift workers were killed
OL,8,Fat the warehouse in Kotovsk and 25
OL,9,Fothers were wounded, Tambov regional
OL,10,FGovernor Yevgeny Pervyshov said.
OL,12,FA total of 61 people were wounded in
OL,13,Fthe Moscow region, Vorobyov said: 20
OL,14,Fsought outpatient care, while 40
OL,15,Fothers were hospitalised. One person
OL,16,Fdied of their injuries, he said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
