OL,3,CUkrainian drones hit warehouses of
OL,4,CRussia's largest online retailer and
OL,5,Coil site
OL,7,FOne more person was killed and another
OL,8,Fwounded in a Ukrainian drone attack on
OL,9,FRussia's Belgorod region on Saturday
OL,10,Fafternoon, according to local
OL,11,Fauthorities.
OL,13,FUkrainian President Volodymyr
OL,14,FZelenskyy said in a Telegram post on
OL,15,FSaturday that Ukrainian long-range
OL,16,Fstrikes hit two "significant
OL,17,Flogistical facilities in the Moscow
OL,18,Fand Tambov regions".
