OL,3,CUkrainian drones hit warehouses of
OL,4,CRussia's largest online retailer and
OL,5,Coil site
OL,7,F"These facilities were used by the
OL,8,Faggressor to supply sanctioned
OL,9,Fcomponents for the production of
OL,10,Fdrones and navigation equipment," he
OL,11,Fwrote. An oil facility was also hit,
OL,12,Fhe said.
OL,14,FIn the city of Vladimir, around 110
OL,15,Fmiles east of Moscow, a Ukrainian
OL,16,Fdrone hit a residential building,
OL,17,Fsparking a brief fire, Vladimir
OL,18,FGovernor Alexander Avdeyev said,
OL,19,Fadding that there were no casualties.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@aO]
