OL,3,CUkrainian drones hit warehouses of
OL,4,CRussia's largest online retailer and
OL,5,Coil site
OL,7,FUkrainian forces also conducted
OL,8,Fstrikes against targets in the Sea of
OL,9,FAzov and in occupied territory,
OL,10,FZelenskyy said.
OL,12,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FUkraine's General Staff said in a
OL,18,Fstatement on Saturday that the fuel
OL,19,Fdepot in Noginsk that was targeted
OL,20,Fovernight supplied the Russian armed
OL,21,Fforces.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
