PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1784432922
OL,3,CUkrainian drones hit warehouses of
OL,4,CRussia's largest online retailer and
OL,5,Coil site
OL,7,FIt also reported hitting two tankers,
OL,8,Ftwo floating cranes and a tugboat in
OL,9,Fthe Black and Azov seas, saying the
OL,10,Fvessels were used to transport oil,
OL,11,Ffuel and military cargo.
OL,13,FSeparately, the military said it
OL,14,Fstruck a Project 10410 Svetlyak-class
OL,15,Fpatrol ship in Kerch, describing it as
OL,16,Fthe second vessel of that class hit in
OL,17,Ftwo days, as well as a railway bridge
OL,18,Fover the Bila River near Sabivka in
OL,19,Fthe occupied Luhansk region that it
OL,20,Fsaid Russia uses for military
OL,21,Flogistics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
