OL,3,CUkrainian drones hit warehouses of
OL,4,CRussia's largest online retailer and
OL,5,Coil site
OL,7,FOverall, the Russian Defence Ministry
OL,8,Fsaid its air defences overnight
OL,9,Fintercepted 379 Ukrainian drones over
OL,10,F19 Russian regions, as well as the
OL,11,Fillegally annexed Crimea, the Sea of
OL,12,FAzov and the Black Sea.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
